# gantt
Live Gantt chart for PaiCoop development.

## Usage

### View
Please visit [http://gantt.paicoop.net](http://gantt.paicoop.net) to view the Gantt Chart.

### Edit
Please edit [`index.html`](./index.html) to modify the Gantt Chart. The syntax can be found [here](https://mermaid-js.github.io/mermaid/#/gantt) and you can practice on [this website](https://mermaid-js.github.io/mermaid-live-editor/edit#).
